忽视 neglect /nɪ’ɡlekt/ vt
【解】to not give enough attention to something
【记】消极的(negative)态度或不吸取教训(lecture)，就容易忽视问题
【例】你忽略了我们的建议
you neglect our advice.
他工作太忙了，忽视了自己的健康
He was so busy that he neglect his health.
ignore [ɪg’nɔːr] vt.
