假设 suppose /sə’pəʊz/ vt.
【解】to pretend that something is true
【记】sup + pose 构成（威胁）. suppose 还有“猜想；以为”的意思
【例】假定他是对的
 Suppose he was right
假装 pretend /prɪ’tend/vt.
【解】to behave in a particular way, in order to make other people believe something that
is not true
【记】假装(pretend)向前(pre)冲(tend 趋向)
【例】不要不懂装懂 Don’t pretend to understand it.
act [ækt] vt.
【解】Behave so as to appear to be; pretend to be
【记】actor 演员 act 扮演 act 假装
【例】一开始我假装沉默寡言
I acted dumb at first
减轻 abate /ə’beɪt/ vt.
【解】to become less strong; to make something less strong
【记】使(ate)力量偏离(ab-)，从而减轻
【例】润滑剂可以减轻机器零件之间的摩擦。
