【解】the effect that somebody/something has on the way a person thinks or behaves or
 on the way that something works or develops
【记】in 不安+ fluent 流利的 adj.  因为受到影响了
【例】我不想影响你，你必须自己决定
I don’t influence you . you must decide for yourself.
